About this item

  • LOCKABLE RECLINING SYSTEM: Smoothly glides into an ergonomic zero-gravity position, with removable elastic cords that immediately adjust to your body's weight
  • PORTABLE DESIGN: Lightweight, foldable design makes these an easy addition to your next trip to the park, beach, or your child's next sporting event

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

Amazon Customer
4 Stars
Great chair with a couple of flaws
This was a great deal for 2 chairs. I have a back injury and needed something to sit in my living room and take the pressure off of my back. This works great for that! I love that the head rest is adjustable and makes it pretty comfy. I also like the little tray that attaches. It is easy to put in and take off. Since its a removable tray I wouldnt put a plate of food or anything fairly heavy on it as it probably wouldnt support it well. Its nice for a drink, the tv remote and cell phone.Things I wish I had known prior to purchasing: The metal bar where your feet go is very uncomfortable. A pool noodle is a really easy fix for this.There are knobs to turn on each side of the chair under the arm rests. These are supposed to lock the chair in place. They do not work very well. Many times I get myself into position, lock it, and after a couple of minutes the chair starts sitting back up. It did the same for my husband. It takes some trial and error to get the chair to stay.
